    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229420/extras/71b5346d97fcff0c4a3ac89dfb29f875.avif?t=1771870967\" width=616 height=190 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>三位英雄，一件被盗的宝物，一场穿越钢铁与秘密的旅程。某种古老的存在正在悄然苏醒。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Danger World》是一款精心打造的回合制 RPG，融合了经典冒险氛围、紧凑的战斗节奏与充满分支的剧情体验。<br><br>首发版本暂不支持中文，但我们会根据愿望单数量优先添加语言支持。请将本作加入愿望单，帮助我们了解中文玩家的需求！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>跟随三位冒险者踏上充满抉择的冒险之路</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当小镇的神圣宝石失窃，Belle、Amelia 和 Wren 展开追查之旅，却意外卷入更大的阴谋。他们将穿越森林与遗迹，对抗被腐化的机械，揭开尘封的谜团。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229420/extras/69065305f9a6e04e0962600ecbf03512.avif?t=1771870967\" width=616 height=220 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>运筹帷幄，重拳出击。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Danger World》采用快节奏的回合制战斗，三位角色风格独特：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Belle 抗伤前排，雷霆反击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Amelia 迅捷突击，精准收割。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wren 大剑横扫，范围压制。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有技能树，没有数值堆叠，每场战斗都重视时机与抉择。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自由抉择</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从河边村落到古代遗迹，你的旅程中处处是选择与后果。你是帮助村民，还是追查敌人？你走的路线会改变故事发展，也将决定最终战斗的准备情况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的每个抉择，最终都将影响决战的走向。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229420/extras/415f5dc295c86943c30103abda1a7d9a.poster.avif?t=1771870967\" width=616 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229420/extras/415f5dc295c86943c30103abda1a7d9a.webm?t=1771870967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229420/extras/415f5dc295c86943c30103abda1a7d9a.mp4?t=1771870967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索濒临崩溃的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一支黑暗军团正在横扫大地，唤醒原本被封印的力量。三位英雄或许是最后的防线——但唯有抢在灾难前采取行动，才有机会阻止一切。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>告别枯燥肝，尽享纯粹冒险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有无聊的刷怪，没有浪费时间的战斗。每场战斗都推进剧情，每个选择都意义非凡。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每个选择，都会留下痕迹</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走出你在《Danger World》中的旅程。路线分歧，选择将产生涟漪，你救了谁（或没有救），你的每个选择都可能改变未来。<br><br><strong>这，就是《Danger World》。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229420/extras/244d690cd058355abfb0cef2aa5fdaae.poster.avif?t=1771870967\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229420/extras/244d690cd058355abfb0cef2aa5fdaae.webm?t=1771870967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
